Date: Fri, 19 May 95 22:20:45 mdt
From: "FYLANXX0" <FYLANXX0@ccmail.wcc.com>
Subject: Please help explain why I could not plot the correct graph
To: xpsoft@shadow.net

     Dear Sir/Madam;
     
     I am sending this file to you to see if you can help me to generate 
     the network graphical plot.
     
     When I used EXPORT GRAPHICS and send the plot to a laser printer, I 
     can only get the nodes and the labels with the nodes.  However, I 
     could not get the lines (links) and their labels plotted.  I don't 
     know what the problem was.
     
     I'd really like to know the answer as soon as possible.  If you can 
     generate a DXF file, could you please send it to me.
     
     Thank you very much

